ZM Krusty Krab A3
=================
By FireWavezZ
-------------

[Old Version _a2 HERE](http://www.gamebanana.com/csszm/maps/161560 "Version a2")


This map is made like the original Krusty Krab from the tv series Spongebob.
The Indoor of the Krusty Krab is allmost the same, i have made some custom props for it, with help from Gmaps.

The map has 64 spawn points, secrets, cade rooms, iron curtains and jellyfish if you are bored.

###### Link to all models and prefabs i made for this map: [Models download on Gamebanana](http://www.gamebanana.com/prefabs/5818 "Models")


I hope you enjoy this submission my fellow zombie players. have fun!


thanks to www.firewallCS.net / *-=Leb=-

IP: 206.212.243.130:27015

A2 Changes:

- Fixed major FPS drop on spawn
- Fixed a few spots that were unfair
- Added Trail to HEgrenade(Green) Deagle(yellow)
- Added background music in KK (thanks to Gmaps)

A3 Changes (on request):

- added 3d skybox
- fixed clips
- the hardest secret is now legal, as easy as for zombie and human.
- more optimised
- changed camp spots here and there


And remember keep going in tubes!
